name: mini yipyip fob
notes:
this is a free pattern for the wee version of the yipyip - can be used as a keychain or purse/backpack fob or mini hanger if you add a chain at the top.

super cute and ridiculous!! share joy straight off the hook!

any size 4 yarn will do - i have used a variety of brands and generally speaking scrap amounts will also suffice - a great way to get through your stash!!

the pattern contains a link to the youtube tutorial if you run into any tricky bits just go watch!

enjoy!!
